title: Easy VPN (Pro) v1.8 Android
description:
Easy VPN (Pro) v1.8
Requirements: 4.0 and up
Overview: A VPN service to access blocked internet websites and secure your connection.

========= Features =============
* No Ads
* Easy to use, Just One button
* Acess all blocked websites like YouTube,Twitter, Torrents with high speed.
* No root access required.

========= How to Use ===========
Open "Easy VPN " app and click on Black button.
VPN service will start connecting to servers,.
You will be shown a system dialog to allow access to app. Check the " I trust this application" and click on "Ok"
VPN service will show status as connected with Green Icon.
Now you are connected. Minimize the app and start browsing your favorite websites.

This app has no advertisements
